data.description: Welcome to 21818 Red Arbor, a beautiful 3 bedroom- 2 1/2 bath single-family property. This 2019-built home boasts a spacious open concept floor plan, perfect for entertaining. The kitchen features granite countertops and overlooks the living room, creating a seamless flow. Downstairs, your guests will have access to a conveniently located half bathroom. Upstairs, you will find 3 bedrooms and two full bathrooms, including a primary bedroom with a HUGE closet. The backyard is ideal for hosting friends, family, and pets. With no previous flooding, this home offers peace of mind. Located in Arbor Trails, you'll have access to exceptional schools, major highways, golf, restaurants, amenities, and top shopping. Don't miss the opportunity to call this beauty your own! Contact us today to schedule a viewing.
